c: 28
v: 82
t: "Futhi labo ababefisa isikhundla sakhe ngayizolo baqala bathi, “Oh ngempela! NguMvelinqangi owandisa isabelo kunoma ngabe ngubani amthandayo ezincekwini zakhe noma asinciphise (isabelo), ukube uMvelinqangi wayengenawo umusa kuthina wayezokwenza ukuthi umhlaba usigwinye, Oh labo abangakholwa! angeke baphunyeleliswe"